Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp53}　{\fsp1}Cream Stew{\r}\N好不容易做的奶油雜燴都涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它熱一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的煩死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為大丈夫是不會向妹妹的攻擊屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這把刀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿夏樹這傢伙沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹還真有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是佩服的時候  我正心煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也吃完飯再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我得早點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹那傢伙太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在今天來這兒之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去千秋家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室掃除誰來做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來後自然會做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天正巧想早點洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話  讓我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為大丈夫要在極近的距離躲過妹妹的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底接不接受妹妹的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  夏樹君曾這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近覺得冬馬舉止越來越像假小子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係  冬馬變得男性化的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也會用對待男生的態度對待她的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  冬馬變得像女生一點他就不會生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  找什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這張這麼女生的照片作為證據給夏樹看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次午睡後照的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回可不像假小子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快生氣的時候就給他看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿這照片給他看沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆不惹他生氣不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑去做什麼了  不成體統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯燉肉都已經不成樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它熱一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說好會早點回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:11:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈真有你的  沒生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過幾天就是冬馬生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒正經送過什麼禮物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說的  我可有過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哥哥  LOVE）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必冬馬那時很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為那玩意兒的反作用才使得冬馬變成這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送的才合她心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（戀愛診斷  GAME）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要送那種玩意給不久前還上幼稚園的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許現在還用不著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會派上用場的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天？我…我堅決不認可這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙最喜歡我的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為經常陪冬馬玩遊戲  所以我非常瞭解她的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那遊戲機都已經被你玩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬當時大失所望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼送什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:12:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想瞭解下頭兒的最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一代是我們家的春香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代是阿優
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四代是藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼二代是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該上高一了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彙報二代頭兒事蹟之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一讓學校第一的小混混南夏樹束手無策的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  頭兒風範十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  南夏樹是你家親戚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是親戚喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是遺憾  沒有什麼特別的情報了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二代頭兒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹那眼神的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘帶錢包了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  好難為情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我客氣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我吃章魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少吃一頓沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然忘帶錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說夏樹  你想的事全寫在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒被那樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼試著打我一拳  絕對打不到我喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打中了  午餐算我請你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為男人欠錢必還
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我才說的那麼巧妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為男人絕不打女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希你少來  這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不那絕對是真的  那時候我可稱的上是天才呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真希嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹這眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像對著自己所憧憬的年長女性那樣深情地望著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你向我要求成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你用那種眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可以的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是仁美嗎  怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  失…失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是你把她弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示自己被誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:12.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弾む鼓動とジャンプしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:12.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}情緒激動地跳了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軽やかなスピードで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這輕快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日だって突き抜けちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛能穿越明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心変わりもご愛嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:23.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}改變心意也有可愛之處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せのアンテナは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸福的天線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一つじゃ足りないです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}豈能只有唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:36.12,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}七色ツバサ広げて　願いを届けに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:36.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開七色翅膀  去傳達願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:43.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑顔の磁石　ハートにぎゅっと　急がなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:43.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歡笑的磁鐵  揪緊內心  必須加快速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.11,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうだっ！ハチャメチャ元気に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沒錯！  用不可思議的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.95,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ハッピー集めちゃいましょ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.95,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來收集幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:56.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真面目じめじめ悩んでないで　カラッと笑い飛ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:56.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要認真地在那煩惱糾結  爽朗地一笑而過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:02.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ぐっと↑ポジティブシンキング　絶対カラフル宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:02.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}GOOD↑積極思考  絕對絢麗多彩的宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:06.40,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}志を打ち上げろ　GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:06.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}表露志向  GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.37,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来ロケット駆けてく　追いつけ追い越せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.37,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}衝向未來的火箭  追上去趕超吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊  社團方面的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…怎麼樣才能變得成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你不問春香而來問我真是找對人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  想必真希學姐也在努力想變得成熟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不爽  這事還是去找成熟的春香問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保…保坂學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香確實向著成熟邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為她處於必須要接受別人的撒嬌的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她內心深處肯定渴望著能向誰撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…保坂學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼拿著傘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼全身濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在二年級的教室前面遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天突然下起了雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我又沒帶傘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摯愛的人  帶傘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一忘帶的話  我就默不作聲地把傘遞給她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不由自主冒著大雨把家裡最好的傘拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛把扣子解開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了隨時能奉上雨傘  我就等在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱氣…還有潮氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你們所見  我的舉手投足都是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  水濺過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的成熟就是奉上雨傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹那眼神  肯定是忘記帶傘正傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘帶傘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借給你  來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的太丟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有把塑料傘  別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此不如借我那把塑料傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿去  來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色…兔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹這眼神…猶如散發著希望的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救啦  放晴了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香莫非你忘記帶傘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  妹妹們忘帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是妹妹們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  來  這是生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  夏樹沒生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  多虧了春香呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  沒什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～歡迎回來～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是極密情報
